<item>
            <title>[LU-18597] statahead: statahead thread doesn&apos;t stop on unmount</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18597</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The visible problem is that Lustre FS mounted on the client is unable to unmount. The umount command hangs forever and also unable to kill it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Stack trace for the umount command&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] ll_kill_super+0x6d/0x140 [lustre]
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] lustre_kill_super+0x32/0x50 [lustre]
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] deactivate_locked_super+0x38/0xb0
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] deactivate_super+0x44/0x50
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] cleanup_mnt+0x150/0x1d0
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] __cleanup_mnt+0x12/0x20
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] task_work_run+0x6a/0xb0
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] exit_to_user_mode_loop+0x157/0x160
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] exit_to_user_mode_prepare+0xa0/0xb0
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] syscall_exit_to_user_mode+0x27/0x50
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] do_syscall_64+0x69/0xc0
[&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;] entry_SYSCALL_64_after_hwframe+0x62/0xcc &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at the code ll_kill_super() waits for all the statahead threads to exit. All the 16 threads are stuck:&lt;/p&gt;
